Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FORGIVE ME, LUVELLIA-SENPAI!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzen seijin ni nante nare yashinai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanben shippai shite naori mo shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushiyoumonai shi datte datte muri datta shi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konna hazu janai tte genjitsutouhi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:01:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mata shinitakunaru konna jibun, iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusagikonde uso o tsuite kizutsuita tte naite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maigo no kanjou dakishimete nemuttemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koukai zenzen zenzen zenzen kienai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitorikiri de kubi shimeai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzen seijin ni nante nare yashinai \Nitsumo risou ni zasetsu shite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzen seijin ni nante nare yashinai \Nitsumo risou ni zasetsu shite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibun semeru pose dake totte oyasui \Nmenzai nigirishimete amaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibun semeru pose dake totte oyasui \Nmenzai nigirishimete amaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanben shippai shite naori mo shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hansei bakari de kawarenakute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokorogoroshi yarisugosu owaranai \Nzange to yuuutsu no yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokorogoroshi yarisugosu owaranai \Nzange to yuuutsu no yoru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzen na jibun ga dokonimo inai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitei na jibun shika mitsukaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first date in ages, just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:06.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9: Peter Grill and \Nthe Treaty's Aftermath
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I let this happen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Piglette!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...brings you he
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished preparing dinner,\Nand I've been awaiting your return...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just checking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do know what a "rest day" is, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware of the implications!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I wash your back for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter, Sir Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the biggest scumbag on the planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was my special date \Nwith Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went behind her back and did\Nall sorts of despicable things...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart breaks for you, Sir Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've gone through a dreadful ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please... try to put your mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the others,\NI would never do anything to cause you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piglette...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, for right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your feelings out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept you for who you are, \Nregardless of your flaws!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pulling me in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold out much long
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There goes the treaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear... How distasteful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a shameless violation of the treaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Farm animal" is an appropriate \Ntitle for an Orc like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't take your eyes off \Nher for a second, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W... Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the three of you are the ones intruding\Nupon Sir Peter's personal time in broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no position to criticize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did the dimwitted Orc...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...anticipate us gettin' \Nthe jump on each other...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is not to be trifled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ignored the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite cheating the system...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They refuse to take responsibility,\Nand now they're trying to pin the blame on each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the extenuating circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way outta this mess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with the guidelines...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall share his fluids equally...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHY DOES THIS KEEP HAPPENING?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does "rest day" mean nothing to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the treaty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it's nothing more than\NA WORTHLESS PIECE OF PAPER!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he might have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This poses a serious problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My sincerest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'see, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we break the rules,\Nthe treaty doesn't exactly specify any kind of punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've reached the point of no\Nreturn in every possible way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of this madness...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should run away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere far, far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put an end to it once and for all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye forever, Luvellia-senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, Peter Grill,\Nthe strongest man in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cast aside everything and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alas, misfortune struck...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In his fragile mental state,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter found himself unable to\Nabandon the life he had come to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring myself to throw it all away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to leave my relationship\Nwith Luvellia-senpai behind...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain has chosen an inopportune\Nmoment to fall upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's an Ogre...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are so inclined, please use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem you have \Nsuffered a great tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an embarrassing story...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall lend an ear, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I've made a terrible mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many, many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point,\NI probably oughtta suck it up and walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, I can't \Nget her out of my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is beyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As fate would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just arrived in this town as part of my\Nsearch for the woman who stole my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman who stole your heart...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years I've been journeying across the land,\Nleaving no stone unturned in a quest to find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows what it's like to fall\Nhead-over-heels for someone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I secured a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, she has become a member of the\NYakeppachi Warriors Guild located in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I am unfamiliar with the details of your situation,\Nyou mustn't let fear consume you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your love is genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I am confident that the gods\Nshall light your path with their blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has such kindness and\Ncompassion for a total stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ogre is the definition of "wholesome"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the future \Nholds... I'll see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai and I are gonna\Nfind our happily-ever-after!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the rain has let up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take my leave accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm a member of the\NYakeppachi Warriors Guild myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask the name of the\Nwoman who stole your heart...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is known to the people of Ogrestan\Nas both our strongest warrior and Princess Royal:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have travelled here in \Npursuit of Lady Lisa Alpacas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpacas is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PRINCESS?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajimari wa tada no koigokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizukeba yuiitsumuni no yoridokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onaji toki kizami toshi o torou yo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Korekara wa onegai sa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long time tonari ni ite eikyuu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatakai no hibi ni tsukaretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikari no ame ni furaretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nureteshimau naraba mayowazu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ore ga kawari ni anata no kasa to naru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samukunai yo tonari ni iru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada soredake de
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wa boku no yoridokoro sa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sono egao ni mata iyasareru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekaijuu sagashitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawari nante inai
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wa boku no yoridokoro sa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soko ni iru dake de mata mitasareru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna ni kizutsuitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mi sasage mamoru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Sir Peter Grill,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little birdie told me that things are gettin'\Nprecarious in the Ogres' neck of the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:11.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10: Peter Grill \Nand the Angry Megaton Axe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'think something bad happened...?